                     Bureau of Transportation Statistics

                         Airline On-Time Statistics
         Summary Statistics   Detailed Statistics   Special Reports

   Use this page to find information from the Bureau of Transportation
   Statistics on flight delays, cancellations and diversions for the
   nation's major airlines and the airports they serve since 1997.

   Summary Statistics.  Search for the average on-time performance record
   for major airlines, for airports served by those carriers and for
   individual flights by number. You can find
     * percentage of flights delayed, canceled or diverted
     * details about departure and arrival delays for late flights
     * departure and arrival performance for all flights

   Detailed Statistics.  Search for more detailed departure and arrival
   statistics, airborne times, cancellations and diversions.

   Special Reports.  View information from the Bureau of Transportation
   Statistics about specific time periods or events, such as Thanksgiving,
   Winter Holiday and Presidents Day Air Travel Delays.


